 I will accept your testimony.\u201d Two men repented and Abu Bakrah did not repent,\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/scholars-ulema\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":3654,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/07\/13\/prophet-daiya-dawah-taxes\/","url_meta":{"origin":34191,"position":4},"title":"Umar II on Da&#8217;wah: The Prophet is caller to Allah, not tax collector","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"July 13, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Ibn Kathir reported: Umar ibn Abdul Aziz, may Allah be pleased with him, said, \u201cVerily, Allah has only sent Muhammad, peace and blessings be upon him, as a preacher. He did not send him as a tax collector.\u201d Source: al-Bida\u0304yah wal-Niha\u0304yah 13\/667 \u0639\u0646 \u0627\u0628\u0646 \u0643\u062b\u064a\u0631 \u0642\u0627\u0644 \u0639\u0645\u0631 \u0628\u0646 \u0639\u0628\u062f \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0632\u064a\u0632\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/scholars-ulema\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":34608,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2020\/11\/30\/umar-ii-humility-allah\/","url_meta":{"origin":34191,"position":5},"title":"Umar II on Humility: Best Muslims are humble with Allah","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"November 30, 2020","format":false,"excerpt":"Al-Ghazali reported: Umar ibn Abdul Aziz, may Allah have mercy on him, said, \u201cThe best people are those who are humble before Allah.\u201d Source: Ih\u0323ya\u0304\u2019 Ulu\u0304m al-Di\u0304n 3\/355 \u0639\u